{"tid":1534653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷搭黨鐵教學","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:27:07.000Z","uid":136992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04eebaf49e85076d281a1539fefa4cba5663f460","tid":1534653,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"大家口口聲聲話罷搭黨鐵 <br />\n但去跳閘 都係要乘搭黨鐵<br />\n鐵路始終有其好處，快捷方便，每次可載大量乘客<br />\n但有時間選擇既你，點解唔幫手罷搭<br />\n有藍同事 831晚話唔識搭巴士返屋企 淨係識搭港鐵<br />\n我就諗起呢兩個app<br />\n利申：連仔我非幫手賣廣告<br />\nmoovit <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtedrf8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtedrf8.png&h=7f3c369f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncitymapper <br />\n我以citymapper 為例子<br />\n你可以點對點，或者set好公司/屋企去進行search<br />\n以大西北屯門去ifc 為例子<br />\n行車時間加等車時間 <br />\n大約要多30分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2k8e9U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2k8e9U.png&h=68cc8ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以荃灣去尖沙咀另一例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Seh6Mg0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeh6Mg0.png&h=589f9364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係要逼你全部罷搭<br />\n你返工/放工 出多30分鐘時間改搭巴士/小巴<br />\n已經個人上令黨鐵少左一半生意<br />\n我知道香港人返工時間好長 搭車時間好長<br />\n但唔差在個半小時<br />\n我承諾，搭少一半黨鐵"},{"pid":"e8ce3bbdcc7359857eb9b936aa7d51552a4975d0","tid":1534653,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0331c0774a6c6c826e7ea449058d4f34c7908092","tid":1534653,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=f6f419cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"ef1eb2f369b965e98f0decf5d7077a2f68e41e6f","tid":1534653,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5742ec1e524b07a9ddec4a4acea53020f4dabcc7","tid":1534653,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}